sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant API as API Gateway
  participant T1 as T1 Transformer Intent Interface
  participant L1 as L1 Full Encoder
  participant L2 as L2 Real-Time Learning
  participant L3 as L3 Active Canvas
  participant L4 as L4 Sparse Activation + Meta-Controller
  participant L5 as L5 Invention Engine
  participant L6 as L6 Multi-Index Retrieval
  participant L7 as L7 Abstraction Engine
  participant L8 as L8 Latent World Model
  participant L9 as L9 Reasoning Bridge
  participant T2 as T2 Transformer Render Interface
  participant FB as Feedback

  U->>API: POST /v1/query
  API->>T1: interpret chaotic language to Semantic IR
  T1-->>API: bounded IR + hypotheses
  API->>L1: encode raw input to structured signature
  API->>L2: integrate memory, indexes, SPPE, world-model candidates
  API->>L3: activate one-shot Canvas when needed
  API->>L4: route cognitive path
  API->>L5: generate bounded invention candidates when novel
  API->>L6: retrieve entity, semantic, temporal, causal, importance indexes
  API->>L7: form abstractions and analogies
  API->>L8: activate causal world-model rules
  API->>L9: simulate, validate, resolve gaps, build VCO
  API->>T2: render VCO to fluent language
  T2-->>API: response + gaps + citations + trace
  API-->>U: auditable response
  U->>API: POST /v1/feedback
  API->>FB: update importance, review queues, controller signals
